      "content": "i know, i know, i should talk to my doctor but i'm not seeing him until next week and i'm literally exhausted right now. i just mean like, melatonin is just a natural supplement right? it's not like a heavy drug. wouldn't adding it to the zolpidem just make it work a little more effectively so i can finally get some rest? it seems like a safe combo since they both do the same thing.",
